<a href="http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/business/Already-on-the-rise--non-traditional-crops-mount-new-export-platform_17145046" target="_self">http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/business/Already-on-the-rise--non-traditi...</a></p><p><i>Bigpictureagriculture.com</i>, ‘Sweet potatoes gaining as regular potatoes losing ground’, 28 August 2014</p><p>
<a href="http://www.bigpictureagriculture.com/2014/08/sweet-potatoes-are-gaining-as-regular-potatoes-are-losing-ground.html" target="_self">http://www.bigpictureagriculture.com/2014/08/sweet-potatoes-are-gaining-...</a></p><p>Jamaica Information Service, ‘Agriculture ministry moves to boost non-traditional exports’, 25 April 2014</p><p>
